Judul: X BRAND PERFORMANCE ASSESSMENT BY USING BRAND BUILDING MODEL APPROACH
Abstrak: The objective of this research was to analyze current X Brand Performance by using Brand Building Model. The model consists of three dimensions, which are Positioning the Brand, Communicating the Brand Message, and Delivering the Brand Performance. This objective was done by comparing the factors influenced in reaching good performance of internet service brand performance according to internet users' perspectives and how customers perceived X in performing those factors. In each of dimensions, X Brand should make an excellent performance to achieve strong brand.
